    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has clearly been well-cared for by its previous owners. The exterior maintains a strong shine and the body is straight, though there are some minor stone chips on the front bumper and a few light surface scratches consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is clean and free of any major wear, with all electronics and mechanical systems functioning as they should. It drives smoothly and has a solid maintenance record, making it a reliable choice for its next owner.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
